project_descr: An Initiative for Greater UN Coherence in Afghanistan

outputs.output_descr: Develop and institute stronger coherence among the UN system in Afghanistan in support of the development priorities on the government of Islamic Republic of Afghanistan. The One UN process, more commonly referred to as "Delivering as One (DaO)", is a long term investment, initiated at the request of the host government. This process has been piloted in eight countries and has been adopted, whole or in party by another six countries.

project_title: an initiative for greater un coherence in afghanistan
